        {
          "username": "Jenniffer Medina",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "111500665490423869294",
          "user_review_count": 36,
          "user_photo_count": 6,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL01JiX-HON1FspsSmeSt8ylIb3mGdTYcUpjUqgP7hA6IDhGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I want to express my sincere gratitude for the excellent care my mom received at this hospital. It was truly a 10 out of 10 experience in every sense.\n\nFrom the very beginning, the service was impeccable. The valet parking team was kind and efficient, making our arrival smooth and stress-free. The front desk and registration staff treated us with respect, patience, and a genuine willingness to help at all times.\n\nOne thing I truly appreciated is that every step of the process was explained with complete clarity, which gave us a great sense of comfort and confidence throughout.\n\nThe nurses were outstanding\u2014attentive, caring, and always paying close attention to every detail. They also explained every instruction clearly and patiently, making sure we fully understood everything, which made a huge difference in our experience.\n\nThe doctors demonstrated a high level of professionalism, explaining everything clearly and showing a true commitment to their patients\u2019 well-being.\n\nI would especially like to recognize Dr. Nana Sarpong, who is simply exceptional. His compassion, professionalism, dedication, and the way he communicates made a remarkable difference. He is a doctor who truly inspires trust and shows genuine passion for what he does.\n\nOverall, the entire team exceeded our expectations. You can truly feel the compassion, dedication, and excellence in service at this hospital.\n\nThank you for taking such wonderful care of my mom. Highly recommended!",
