          "description": "Being 70 years old, I have had a plethora of experience with hospitals. Mostly concerning family and friends. So I know what I\u2019m talking about when it comes to such facilities.\nMilstein is an excellent facility. My brother spent a week here recovering from pneumonia. Everyone he encountered was professional and exhibited the utmost care and concern. Several times when he hit the button for help, an attendant magically appeared within seconds. It\u2019s clean, quiet and the place to be, if you must.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kSGEyTnBZMGQ2ZHpKb1FYaHJkMWx4YVdOMlNuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x27bff071752b797d!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmdHa2NpY0d6dzJoQXhrd1lxaWN2Snc%7C%7C?hl=en",
