          "description": "NewYork-Presbyterian Milstein Hospital in particular interventional radiology is the most incompetent crowd(i can call them medical professionals). If you want actual treatment DO NOT COME HERE. Nobody does anything and nobody knows anything. The procedure was scheduled for 12 pm, we were told to come at 11 am in order not to delay. it started at 1 pm because of that delay we were late to the treatment center and could not start IV treatment. But guess what, I was able to go to mychart and download and after visit summary at 12:15 pm. The procedure didn't even start but \"You saw Alyssa Villafana; ERNST GARCON; and Luis De La Cruz on Thursday November 13, 2025. The following issues were addressed: \" isn't that amazing? Incompetent facility with incompetent bunch of,I dont even know what to call them. Im sitting right next to the procedure room and people walk in and out during the procedure with the light in use on and radiation sign telling that Caution Radiation Area.",
